data.description: If you're dreaming of country living where you can spread out but are close to town, you found the one! This home has so many things to offer, one spectacular feature is the detached workshop which could be a mechanic's dream or suit any of your handy projects! Inside the home, be impressed with lots of space, downstairs you'll find a large family room that is open to a flex room that could be either a formal dining or an office. The kitchen has been partially updated with appliances and a long bar table and additional cabinets, as well as a breakfast area overlooking the serene backyard. There is a fifth bedroom downstairs that has a separate exterior door which also offers lots of options. Full bath downstairs with shower/tub combo. Large laundry room with plenty of cabinets for storage and oversized side entry garage. The sellers had started updating the floors and have left lots of flooring so the new owner can continue the vision. Upstairs, enter the primary bedroom through elegant double doors; the primary bath shines with double vanity, jetted tub, separate shower and not one but two walk in closets. There are 2 additional bedrooms on the same side as the primary, they are connected by a barn door, with smart storage feature built in. The fourth bedroom is down the hall with built in corner nook seating as well as a built in desk. The upstairs hall bath has been completely updated and modernized and looks fantastic. Plenty of space in the backyard and serene views on trees and nature, there is an additional storage building in the back corner. The patio is large and the siding has been recently painted and looks great. Easy access to Fort Cavazos! Copperas Cove Schools. So to sum things up: This is a great deal!
